STRATOPLEX IS MY NEW FLAGSHIP GAME FOR MY GAMES EMPIRE!

                ******************
   ******************************************

First, because this is a two disk game, for Stratoplex to run, you MUST rename your disks:

        The first disk MUST be called "StratoDemoA"
        The second disk MUST be called "StratoDemoB"

    Also, The program MUST be run from the first disk, because of this, the DEMO doesn't run from CD's or Hard Drives.

The Full Version has a Hard Drive option and the program will autodetect it's proper path name from Hard Drive, so no install program is necessary.  Just make sure both support-file drawers are in the same place as the program and docs, in the hard drive.  The full version also has different names for disks A and B, which must remain the way I have put them.

