STRATOPLEX is the new flagship for my Awesome Armada of games!

 STRATOPLEX is 'THE ULTIMATE GAME IN THE HISTORY OF THE UNIVERSE'.

   STRATOPLEX has 7 sequences in total, and 3 of which were inspired by the Disney movie TRON, but they only made 2D video game versions of TRON, in which people for the last dozen years have ALWAYS FAILED to surpass the 1982 original arcade game.  Then, about 15 yeasr later, in late 1996, a game worthy of being called the sequal to the MOVIE ITSELF was created by Pete W Storonskij! (oops, that was conceited :)

   TRON is a trademark of Disney Corporation, World Rights Reserved,  No TRON graphics ever appear anywhere in my game : Stratoplex: Lightning Fury

   I also did a 3D ASTEROID BELT sequence for the fun of it.

   One of the other 3 sequences is STRATEGEMA, directly from the second season of STARTREK: THE NEXT GENERATION (TM) (STARTREK is a trademark of Paramount Pictures Corporation).  Remember when Data played the video game with the Kalrami Strategic Master (and then the annoying Ferengi attacked them), well, now you too can try your hand at this game.  Accurately converted to computers for the first time ever.

No Star Trek graphics ever appear anywhere in my game: Stratoplex: Lightning Fury

   The remaining two sequences are like nothing you have ever seen before, and that is because I have invented them!!!  There is my Patented Shield Configuration Sequence, where you must tightly surround your ship with your energy shield, in order to gain more shields.  My shield modulation sequence is an industry first, and is copyright © 1988, 1996 Pete W Storonskij, World Rights Reverved.  My other sequence is my Patented Weapon Modulation Sequence!!!!!!!  These sequences tax your brain to it's limits while giving you a much needed rest from the lightning fast and furious TRON-Style action.  Actually, they will drive you crazy, but that's ok too.

   You can only die in the 3D sequences, but if you fail one of the other sequences, you're chances of death in the 3D sequences goes up substantially.

   Oh yeah, the three sequences that I made into 3D FIRST:

   The 'TRON LIGHT CYCLE SEQUENCE' is now in 3D!!!!!!!
   The 'TRON TANK MAZE SEQUENCE' is now in 3D!!!!!!!
   The 'TRON MCP CONE SEQUENCE' is now in 3D!!!!!!!

   The 3D MCP Cone sequence has the convenient advancing wall behind you, always pushing you ever closer to the sawtoothed spinning wavefront walls.  If you survive this, you must destroy the Main Reactor at the end of the tunnel.

   In the 3D Tron Tank sequences, you get to destroy wandering Tornadeuxs and you also get to destroy Power Generators that hold the key to winning the game!  Watch your weapon's fire, since you're weapon overheats quickly.

   The 3D algorithms give you an unprecedented view of the Stratoplex's internal architecture while the radar display gives you only enough information to keep the game going along smoothly.

   Stratoplex is the first game to accurately simulate realistic Storm Effects.  Tornadoes, Fog, Lightning and Thunder effects are flawlessly executed while you play my game.

   Of course, I pay my greatest respects to Disney Corporation, so I changed the Disney's Tanks, Light Cycles (TM), And Recognizers (QED) into MY 'Tornadeux Drones' (TM).  I hereby award Disney Corporation with The Award of Outstanding Achievement in the Field of Excellence (the award Homer Simpson got on the cartoon show).

  You are not a digitized employee of Tron's 'Encom' or Escom, which is a bit of a coincidence, but you are in a giant artificial planet, and you have to destroy it (of course), because some evil alien species have hijacked it from your Thrantoxian shipyards (They do this sort of thing all the time).

   I decided that you get about 10 shields, because this game is HARD, and you will need them.  Shields are useful because you should be allowed more than just one trivial mistake, after all, games are supposed to be fun, like Stratoplex.  My shields are automatic, because you shouldn't be penalised (killed) for not turning them on.  I decided that you get an assortment of weapons, this makes destroying enemies a bit easier.  I also decided to make the enemy artificial intellegence much harder than it has ever been before!

   Did I mention that I, Pete W Storonskij, did it in 3D FIRST!  Actually, as of this writing, 'Stratoplex: Lightning Fury' is the ONLY game in the 3D TRON genre!!!!!!!  In fact, I invented the 3D TRON ACTUAL VIDEO GAME genre, (although Disney thought of the movie and the classic 2D TRON video game, they didn't actually make a 3D TRON video game).  The Apotheosis is STRATOPLEX: Lightning Fury!!!

   STRATOPLEX is the first game equipped with it's own Manifest Destiny!!!!!!!

   This marks the end of the era where light cycle games look like raindrops racing down a window pane!  FROM NOW ON, STRATOPLEX: LIGHTNING FURY IS THE ONLY ONE TO PLAY!!!!!!!

            5 QUARTS OF PURE ADRENALINE!!!!!!!

   STRATOPLEX IS THE PROOF THAT TURNS YOU INTO PUDDING!!!

   STRATOPLEX IS FLUID VELOCITY, THOUGHT-TECTONICS!!!!!!!

   CLEAR YOUR CALENDAR FOR ALL OF NEXT YEAR, YOU WILL BE PLAYING STRATOPLEX!!!

