   The 2D view of everyone else does give you the advantage of the overhead view, but THAT'S TOO EASY, YOU DESERVE A REAL CHALLENGE!  You have played hundreds of 2D versions since 1982 and they have gotten progressively worse than the old arcade game.  I think everyone should have mastered it by now, and I think you are ready for a real challenge.  The challenge of getting completely lost in a maze, not knowing where you are going, and seeing walls accellerate towards you at 500 meters/second is certainly an exhilerating feeling!  Now you know why Stratoplex is so special, it is THE ULTIMATE GAME IN THE HISTORY OF TRHE UNIVERSE!

